source:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
The light-hearted hunter is eager to see what you can do.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
ファノヴの里の陽気なヴィースは、冒険者と狩りに出かけたいようだ。
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_TODO_00<tab>ユキス・ネルの大ピラミッド前にいる陽気なヴィースと話す

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_TODO_01<tab>Use the leather sack on a weakened Greatwood rail.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_TODO_01<tab>弱らせた<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2219901 /var>に<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FC401 /var>を使い捕獲

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the bulging leather sack to the light-hearted hunter.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_TODO_02<tab>陽気なヴィースに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FC501 /var>を渡す
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_TODO_03<tab>ファノヴの里の陽気なヴィースと話す

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_000<tab>Well met, ally of Ronka. Did you hear? Almet's recently returned with an astounding catch.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_000<tab>わぁ、噂のロンカの盟友の人じゃないか！
ねぇねぇ、よければ一緒に狩りにいかない？

TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_001<tab>人使いの荒いアルメに、装束の材料にする用の、
<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2219901 /var>の捕獲を頼まれちゃって……。
5羽もだよ！？　多いよね！？

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_002<tab>Almet is without question one of our greatest hunters, but I am most curious to see how you would fare against them. If you would take up the challenge, meet with me at the Great Pyramid of Ux'ner.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_002<tab>でも、有名人と一緒なら、俄然やる気もでるじゃん？
それに、外の人がどうやって狩りをするのか、興味があるの！
狩場が「ユキス・ネルの大ピラミッド」にあるから、一緒にきて！

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_010<tab>You have come. Very good! I care not for how many you can capture, only how it is done. When you have weakened one, use this sack to capture it and bring it back here.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_010<tab>きてくれてありがと！
じゃあ、ピラミッドの奥にいる「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2219901 /var>」を1羽、
弱らせてから、この「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FC401 /var>」で捕獲してくれる？

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_011<tab>Good luck in your hunt. I will be watching.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_011<tab>うん、1羽でいいよ！　全部取ってきてもらったら悪いし！
アタシは外の人の戦い方を、見せてもらいたいだけだから、
ちょっと離れたところで君の狩りを見てるね！

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_030<tab>I can see now why Almet speaks so highly of you. Your form was unlike anything I have ever seen. But what of the Greatwood rail?
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_030<tab>見てたよ、見事な戦いっぷりだったね！
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FC501 /var>」、も見せてもらってもいい？

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_031<tab>You have done well not to bruise the feathers or the skin. We can make good use of this.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_031<tab>うんうん、羽根や皮への被害も最小限だし……
これなら立派な装束の素材になるよ！
ロンカの盟友たる人は、さすがの腕前だなぁ！

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_032<tab>Yes, such a prize warrants a reward. Meet with me at Fanow and I will see you compensated for your trouble.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_032<tab>よし、これを持って、「ファノヴの里」へ帰ろう！
いい戦いを見せてもらったから、
きちんとお礼しないとね！

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_040<tab>For you, oh great hunter, and ally of Ronka.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_040<tab>はいっ、じゃあこれ、お礼ね！
遠慮なく持っていって！

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_041<tab>I will see this to Almet and─
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_041<tab>私はこの<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FC501 /var>を、
さっそくアルメに……

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_042<tab><gasp> She will ask where is <var 1A 02 /var>my<var 1A 01 /var> quarry!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_042<tab>ああっ！！
自分の分を捕獲するの、忘れてた！！

source: TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_043<tab>What a fool I am. I should have been hunting with you. Perhaps if I can hunt four and offer them together with yours...
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF012_03471_VIISHUNTER03471_000_043<tab>うわああああああん！　アタシ、また狩場に戻らなきゃ！
あと4羽捕獲したら、君が取ってくれた分も、
きちんとアルメに渡すからね、ごめんね！
